{"article_id":"UuGWBQmp6NzkNzz4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Official :","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Intel indicated Bergdahl 's location a few times ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"but it was too risky","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"to get him","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Bergdahl was freed in exchange for 5","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"held at Guantanamo ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"who are moved to Qatar","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Official :","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Bergdahl left on his own","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"but no definitive finding","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"he deserted ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"probe finds","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Some hail the American soldier 's release ,","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"while others criticize the move","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"The Army will conduct `` a comprehensive , coordinated '' review into the case of Sgt . Bowe Bergdahl","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"-- the recently freed soldier","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"whom some have deemed a hero ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"others a deserter --","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"the military branch 's civilian leader announced Tuesday .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Secretary of the Army John McHugh began a statement on Bergdahl 's case","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"by saying","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that `` we are grateful that an American soldier is back in American hands ''","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and insisting","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"`` our first priority is ensuring Sgt . Bergdahl 's health","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and beginning his reintegration process . ''","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"McHugh did n't address specific questions","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"surrounding how the soldier ended up detained in Afghanistan or what he did while in that situation .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"But he did say","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that the military 's review `` will include speaking with Sgt . Bergdahl","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"to better learn from him the circumstances regarding his disappearance and captivity . ''","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"`` All other decisions will be made thereafter , and in accordance with appropriate regulations , policies and practices , ''","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"McHugh said .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Authorities have n't given any indication","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"that such a decision is coming anytime soon .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"Why did Bergdahl leave his outpost ?","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Why did Bergdahl leave his outpost ?","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"02:36","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"President Obama defends Bergdahl rescue","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"President Obama defends Bergdahl rescue","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"02:03","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Carney defends Bergdahl prisoner swap","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Carney defends Bergdahl prisoner swap","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"02:45","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Speaking Tuesday in Warsaw , Poland ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"President Barack Obama said","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"that Bergdahl had not then been interrogated by U.S. officials","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"because he is still undergoing medical care .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Nor had he met yet with his family ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"according to the President .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Bergdahl","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"-- who was released by his Taliban captors in exchange for five prisoners","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"held by the United States at Guantanamo Bay , Cuba --","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"is at Landstuhl Regional Medical Center in Germany .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"The five prisoners headed to Qatar as part of the exchange .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Bergdahl will remain at that U.S. Army medical center in Germany","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"until he completes treatment ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"a U.S. defense official there told CNN .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"After that , Bergdahl will return to the United States","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"and go to a San Antonio military base ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"the official said .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"In his statement Tuesday , McHugh suggested","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Bergdahl 's medical treatment will be a driving force in what happens next and when it does .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"`` There is no timeline for this ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and we will take","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"as long","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"as medically necessary","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"to aid his recovery , ''","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"McHugh said .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"The release of Bergdahl , the last American soldier","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"held captive from the Iraq and Afghanistan conflicts ,","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"spurred celebration in many circles .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"But others challenged the move","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"-- including some critical","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"because he was let go in exchange for Guantanamo detainees ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"plus many of those","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"who served with Bergdahl","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"who characterized him as a deserter","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"whose `` selfish act '' ended up costing others ' lives .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"According to firsthand accounts from soldiers in his platoon ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Bergdahl","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"-- sometime before he was set to go on guard duty --","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"shed his weapons","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and walked off an observation post with nothing more than a compass , a knife , water , a digital camera and a diary .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"The team leader , Evan Buetow , recalled to CNN 's Jake Tapper","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that Bergdahl `` did not agree with the war effort in Afghanistan ''","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"and had said various things","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"that , in retrospect , led him to believe","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"the soldier had `` walked away . ''","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"`` It was a gut feeling","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"I had , ''","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Buetow said Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"`` ... When he comes up missing","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"and all of his sensitive items are left behind ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"it just kind of hit us in the head . ''","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"At least six soldiers were killed in subsequent searches for Bergdahl ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"according to soldiers","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"involved in operations","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"to find him .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"The Pentagon was not able to provide details on specific operations","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"in which any soldiers","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"killed during that time","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"were involved .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Also , many soldiers in Bergdahl 's platoon said","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"attacks seemed to increase against the United States in Paktika province in the days and weeks","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"following his disappearance .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Buetow conceded","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"that he and others may never know","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"if this violence was coincidental","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"or if Bergdahl gave his captors information voluntarily or after being tortured .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"Yet he found it `` incredibly suspicious '' that attacks","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"after Bergdahl disappeared","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"seemed to become `` far more directed . ''","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"As to those U.S. soldiers","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"who died ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Buetow said ,","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"`` Those soldiers would not be on those patrols , in those specific areas","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"when they were killed ,","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"unless Bergdahl left .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"And that 's a fact to me . ''","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"All this said ,","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"the exact circumstances of his disappearance are very uncertain .","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"Published accounts have varied widely , from claims","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"that he walked off the post","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"to claims","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"that he was grabbed from a latrine .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Noting everything","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"that he left behind ,","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"an Army fact-finding investigation","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"conducted in the months after his 2009 disappearance","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"concluded","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"that Bergdahl left his outpost deliberately and on his own free will ,","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"according to a U.S. military official","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"briefed on the report .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"The official spoke to CNN Tuesday on the condition of anonymity","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"due to the sensitive nature of the information .","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"There was no definitive finding","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Bergdahl deserted","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"because that would require knowing his intent","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"-- something","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Army officials could n't do","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"without talking to the soldier .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"The investigation included interviews with members of Bergdahl 's unit ,","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"none of whom reported seeing him go ,","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"the official said .","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"In 2012 , Rolling Stone reported","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"that Bergdahl 's unit had discipline and other issues during its time in Afghanistan .","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"Addressing the matter Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"Obama stressed","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"that we `` we do n't leave men and women in uniform behind ''","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"and insisted","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"prisoner swaps `` happen ... at the end of wars . '' `` Whatever the circumstances may turn out to be , we still get an American soldier back","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"if he is held in captivity .","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"Period .","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"Full stop , ''","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"Obama said .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"`` We do n't condition that . ''","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"Intelligence indicated","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"where Bergdahl was being held a couple of times during his five years in captivity ,","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"a U.S. official said .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"But any mission","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"to get him","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"was deemed too risky","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"-- especially for Berghdal .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"Team leader :","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"Bergdahl 'not a hero '","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"Team leader :","depth":14},{"id":179,"text":"Bergdahl 'not a hero '","depth":14},{"id":180,"text":"02:51","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"Obama defends Bowe Bergdahl swap","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":184,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"Obama defends Bowe Bergdahl swap","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"03:25","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"Cupp :","depth":16},{"id":189,"text":"Bergdahl abandoned his unit","depth":16},{"id":190,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":15},{"id":191,"text":"MUST WATCH Cupp :","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"Bergdahl abandoned his unit","depth":15},{"id":193,"text":"03:54","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":16},{"id":195,"text":"Hagel :","depth":17},{"id":196,"text":"'Unfair ' to judge Bergdahl","depth":17},{"id":197,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"MUST WATCH Hagel :","depth":16},{"id":199,"text":"'Unfair ' to judge Bergdahl","depth":16},{"id":200,"text":"00:59","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"Bergdahl 's squad leader :","depth":17},{"id":203,"text":"He deserted us","depth":17},{"id":204,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":16},{"id":205,"text":"MUST WATCH Bergdahl 's squad leader :","depth":16},{"id":206,"text":"He deserted us","depth":16},{"id":207,"text":"02:18","depth":15},{"id":208,"text":"Instead , the United States worked through a third party","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"to arrange a prisoner swap .","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"The five Taliban prisoners","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"freed from U.S. custody","depth":14},{"id":212,"text":"were transferred to Qatar ,","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"where Obama said","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"he 's confident","depth":14},{"id":215,"text":"they wo n't endanger the United States on the battlefield or elsewhere .","depth":14},{"id":216,"text":"Several factors help mitigate the risk of the exchange ,","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"two senior U.S. officials said .","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"They include :","depth":13},{"id":219,"text":"- They 've been in Guantanamo for a long time","depth":15},{"id":220,"text":"and therefore likely do n't have networks as extensive","depth":16},{"id":221,"text":"as they once had ;","depth":16},{"id":222,"text":"- Most U.S. troops will out of Afghanistan in a year ;","depth":15},{"id":223,"text":"- Personal assurances from Qatar 's emir","depth":16},{"id":224,"text":"to closely monitor them .","depth":16},{"id":225,"text":"The detainees wo n't be under house arrest ,","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"yet one U.S. official says ,","depth":13},{"id":227,"text":"`` We think","depth":14},{"id":228,"text":"the Qataris are going to keep a very , very close eye on them . ''","depth":14},{"id":229,"text":"Asked about why Congress was n't consulted about the exchange ,","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"the President said","depth":11},{"id":231,"text":"that over the years , the White House had talked with Congress about the possible need for such an exchange ,","depth":12},{"id":232,"text":"and that officials had to move quickly","depth":13},{"id":233,"text":"when the opportunity arose .","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"`` This was likely the last , best opportunity","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"to free him , ''","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"White House spokesman Jay Carney told CNN 's Wolf Blitzer ,","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":238,"text":"that `` we did the right thing ''","depth":12},{"id":239,"text":"in negotiating a deal","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"much like `` we exchanged prisoners '' with the Germans and Japanese after World War II .","depth":13},{"id":241,"text":"As to Bergdahl , he is in stable condition at Landstuhl for treatment of conditions","depth":9},{"id":242,"text":"related to five years of captivity ,","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"the hospital said Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":244,"text":"Citing privacy laws ,","depth":9},{"id":245,"text":"the medical center did not provide specifics about his medical condition .","depth":9},{"id":246,"text":"He is undergoing a period of `` reintegration ''","depth":11},{"id":247,"text":"that includes decompression and help from doctors , security officers , lawyers , chaplains , his family and more ,","depth":11},{"id":248,"text":"the hospital said .","depth":10},{"id":249,"text":"`` The goal is to return him to family and society and on the path to complete recovery , ''","depth":11},{"id":250,"text":"the medical center said ,","depth":11},{"id":251,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":252,"text":"that there is no timeline for the recovery process .","depth":11},{"id":253,"text":"McHugh 's comments Tuesday followed those of Chairman of the Joint Chiefs of Staff Gen. Martin Dempsey ,","depth":7},{"id":254,"text":"who stressed","depth":8},{"id":255,"text":"that questions of Bergdahl 's conduct is separate from the effort","depth":9},{"id":256,"text":"to recover any missing U.S. soldier .","depth":9},{"id":257,"text":"`` As for the circumstances of his capture ,","depth":10},{"id":258,"text":"when he is able to provide them ,","depth":10},{"id":259,"text":"we 'll learn the facts , ''","depth":9},{"id":260,"text":"Dempsey said .","depth":8},{"id":261,"text":"`` Like any American , he is innocent until proven guilty . ''","depth":8},{"id":262,"text":"He added :","depth":9},{"id":263,"text":"`` Our Army 's leaders will not look away from misconduct","depth":10},{"id":264,"text":"if it occurred . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":529,"left":279,"right":528,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":279,"left":0,"right":278,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":276,"right":277,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":271,"right":275,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":271,"left":1,"right":270,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":267,"right":269,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":2